query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('azure-active-directory',
'escaping',
'graphql',
'grouping',
'gtk',
'integer',
'ios10',
'jax-rs',
'localhost',
'processing',
'qt4',
'sails.js',
'scrollbar',
'xna');
